Dialogue: 100,0:00:36.13,0:00:37.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我理解不了这个动画,兄弟\N{\rENG}I don't get this cartoon, man.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.73,0:00:40.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}它们为什么不干脆把地上的冰淇淋吃掉呢?\N{\rENG}Why don't they just eat the ice cream off the floor?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.24,0:00:41.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们没必要哭啊\N{\rENG}They don't have to cry about it.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:43.31,0:00:46.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗷,又来了\N{\rENG}Aw, not again.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.14,0:00:48.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}昨天也出现过这种情况\N{\rENG}It was doing this yesterday, too.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.31,0:00:50.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等一下,我能搞定\N{\rENG}Hang on. I got it.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:52.08,0:00:53.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在呢?\N{\rENG}How about now? Aah.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:53.82,0:00:55.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}电视之前从没出现过这种情况\N{\rENG}It's never done that before.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:55.68,0:00:57.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}通过全频段...橄榄石\N{\rENG} On all frequencies...Peridot.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.85,0:00:59.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是橄榄石\N{\rENG} This is Peridot,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.10,0:01:00.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}通过全频段\N{\rENG}transmitting on all frequencies\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.89,0:01:03.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}从已废弃的水晶体系殖民地地球发送信息\N{\rENG}from abandoned crystal system colony planet earth\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:03.26,0:01:04.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}致黄钻石\N{\rENG}to yellow diamond.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.59,0:01:06.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的任务失败了\N{\rENG}My mission has been compromised.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:06.60,0:01:08.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的护送者与线人消失了\N{\rENG}My escort and informant are gone,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.43,0:01:10.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且我现在被困在这里\N{\rENG}and I am now stranded.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:10.18,0:01:11.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一定要派遣支援啊!\N{\rENG}Please send help.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.33,0:01:14.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是橄榄石,通过全频段...\N{\rENG}This is Peridot, transmitting on all frequencies...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:14.40,0:01:15.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好的.谢谢\N{\rENG}Okay. Thanks.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:16.17,0:01:18.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮说她电视上也是这个\N{\rENG}Connie says it's on her TV, too.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.04,0:01:19.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但橄榄石能从哪\N{\rENG}But where could Peridot\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.08,0:01:21.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}传送这么强的信号?\N{\rENG}be broadcasting a signal that strong?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:21.34,0:01:23.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}只有一个地方\N{\rENG}There's only one place.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.76,0:01:31.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}狮子,你还好吗?\N{\rENG}Lion, are you okay?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.95,0:01:33.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}正如我所担心的\N{\rENG}It's as I feared.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.36,0:01:39.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看来橄榄石通过某些手段修复了通讯中枢站\N{\rENG}It looks like Peridot somehow repaired the communication hub.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.09,0:01:41.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}或者,至少也是一部分\N{\rENG}Well, at least some of it.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.43,0:01:44.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以...我们只需要再一次砸坏它,对吧?\N{\rENG}So we just got to wreck it up again, right?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:44.37,0:01:46.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们得融合成苏纪石\N{\rENG}You guys should form Sugilite.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.64,0:01:47.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}...是吗?\N{\rENG}Yeah?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:47.74,0:01:50.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃,我觉得,这得看石榴\N{\rENG}Well, uh, it's up to Garnet, I guess.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:50.77,0:01:53.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你怎么看?我们要不砸个爽?\N{\rENG}What do you say? Shall we mash it up?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:53.46,0:01:54.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不\N{\rENG}No.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:54.48,0:01:57.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但...难道我们不需要像上次一样巨大吗?\N{\rENG}But...Don't we need to be huge like last time?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:57.45,0:01:59.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}上次是场灾难\N{\rENG}Last time was a disaster.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:01:59.20,0:02:01.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}上次我们融合时,苏纪石暴走了\N{\rENG}Last time we fused, Sugilite went berserk.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:01.82,0:02:04.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且归功于她我们之后都没法传送到这了\N{\rENG}And it's because of her that we can't even warp here anymore.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:04.75,0:02:07.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我会变得草率,你则会变得鲁莽\N{\rENG}I could be rash, you could be reckless,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:07.66,0:02:09.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}最后我们都会忘乎所以\N{\rENG}and we could both get carried away.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.73,0:02:15.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以,这次,苏纪石要下场了\N{\rENG}So, for the time being, Sugilite is benched.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.23,0:02:17.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们现在需要的是仔细\N{\rENG}What we need now is to be careful.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.06,0:02:20.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这次该你和我了,珍珠\N{\rENG}It's you and me, Pearl.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:20.77,0:02:21.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}咱们融合吧\N{\rENG}Let's fuse.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:24.57,0:02:25.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不要哭,珍珠\N{\rENG}Don't cry, Pearl.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.00,0:02:30.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来吧,一起完成任务\N{\rENG}Come on. Let's do this.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:30.65,0:02:31.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我跟着你呢\N{\rENG}I'm right behind you.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Whoo-hoo!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:33.16,0:02:35.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}融合,融合,融合,融合!\N{\rENG}Fusion! Fusion! Fusion! Fusion!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.12,0:02:36.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}准备\N{\rENG}Ready.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:38.14,0:02:38.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等\N{\rENG} Hang on.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.29,0:02:41.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}恍如隔世啊\N{\rENG}It's been such a long time.\N
Dialogue: 600,0:02:43.00,0:02:45.00,Hint,,0,0,0,,此处舞蹈参考自韩国歌手sunmi（李宣美），同时与其歌曲Full Moon同步
Dialogue: 100,0:03:10.88,0:03:13.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}观众们晚上好!\N{\rENG}Good evening, everybody!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:15.14,0:03:18.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是可爱的红玛瑙,\N{\rENG}This is the lovely sardonyx, coming to you live\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.79,0:03:21.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在即将彻底报废的通讯中枢为你现场直播\N{\rENG}from the soon-to-be former communication hub.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:21.73,0:03:23.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们今晚怎么样?\N{\rENG}How are y'all doing tonight?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好极了\N{\rENG} Great.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}女巨人!\N{\rENG} Giant woman!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:26.07,0:03:27.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢,我的星星啊\N{\rENG}Oh, my stars.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这不是史蒂文·宇宙吗\N{\rENG}If it isn't Steven Universe.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们总算见面了\N{\rENG}We finally meet.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么...你认为呢?\N{\rENG}So... What do you think?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.37,0:03:33.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等待我值吗?\N{\rENG}Was I worth the wait?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:34.24,0:03:36.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我在说什么瞎话啊?当然啦\N{\rENG}What am I saying? Of course I was.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:38.41,0:03:40.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔,你真能说会道啊\N{\rENG}Wow. You're so articulated.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:40.65,0:03:43.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不也是最可爱的小帅哥吗?\N{\rENG}Well, aren't you the sweetest little charmer?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:43.32,0:03:45.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我现在真想将你在手心挤挤\N{\rENG}I could literally squish you right now.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}反正又不难\N{\rENG}It would not be hard.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.59,0:03:51.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对不起,我实在是太高兴我能来这里了\N{\rENG}Sorry. I'm just so excited to be here.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你知道,我最近一直不能做自己呢\N{\rENG}You see, I haven't exactly been myself lately.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.58,0:03:58.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}融合段子\N{\rENG}Fusion joke.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.67,0:04:02.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我有的,不只是段子\N{\rENG}And jokes aren't the only thing I've got.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.54,0:04:07.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯?哦!\N{\rENG}Hmm?  Oh!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:13.11,0:04:15.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你要用你的战锤砸些东西吗?\N{\rENG}Are you gonna smash stuff with your war hammer?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.68,0:04:18.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"砸"是用来形容\N{\rENG}"Smash" is the word one would use\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.62,0:04:21.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}另外一个人会做的事的词\N{\rENG}to describe what someone else might do.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.60,0:04:23.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在...\N{\rENG}Now...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:23.02,0:04:26.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真正用来形容在下的词是...\N{\rENG}The proper words used to describe yours truly are...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.90,0:04:27.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}明确\N{\rENG}"Specific"...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:29.53,0:04:30.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}聪慧\N{\rENG}..."intelligent"...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.87,0:04:32.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}精准\N{\rENG}"Accurate"...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.20,0:04:33.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}无瑕\N{\rENG}"Faultless"...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}优雅\N{\rENG}..."elegant"...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}得体\N{\rENG}"Controlled"...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.44,0:04:38.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}精妙,风度\N{\rENG}"Surgical," "graceful"...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然还有...\N{\rENG}And...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.21,0:04:43.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}强力!\N{\rENG}"Powerful"!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.04,0:04:48.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但,是的,有时,我也会,砸东西\N{\rENG}But, yes, occasionally, I am known to smash.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.28,0:04:57.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在,大家一定要牢记...\N{\rENG}Now, just remember, everybody...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:57.26,0:04:59.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一旦你有求于可爱的红玛瑙,\N{\rENG}If you ever have need of the lovely sardonyx,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.76,0:05:01.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}要告诉珍珠和石榴哦\N{\rENG}let Pearl and Garnet know.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:01.16,0:05:04.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我立刻就会出现-真的\N{\rENG}I'll be there in a flash -- literally.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.74,0:05:17.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们太棒了!\N{\rENG}You guys were amazing!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们刚才真是这样?哦,那很好啊\N{\rENG}We were? Oh. Well, that's good.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.85,0:05:21.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们赞爆了!\N{\rENG}We were awesome!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.48,0:05:25.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们为什么不经常这么做?\N{\rENG}Why don't we do that more often?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.75,0:05:28.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么,梨?为什么要对我撒谎?\N{\rENG}Why, pear? Why did you lie to me?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.66,0:05:32.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不是故意的\N{\rENG} I didn't mean to.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢,梨\N{\rENG}Aw. Pear.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:33.76,0:05:35.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我会原谅她.你呢?\N{\rENG}I'd forgive her. Wouldn't you?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.58,0:05:36.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Mm.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.08,0:05:39.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔,嘿,紫晶\N{\rENG}Oh, hey, Amethyst.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你要错过"哭泣早餐朋友"了\N{\rENG}You're missing "crying breakfast friends."\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.44,0:05:42.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没什么\N{\rENG}That's okay.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:42.70,0:05:43.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我很好\N{\rENG}I'm fine.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.87,0:05:46.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但这集目前为止非常好看\N{\rENG}But it's a really good one so far.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.11,0:05:47.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}并不\N{\rENG}Not really.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:47.14,0:05:49.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别担心,我在录制,可以待会看\N{\rENG}Don't worry. I'm recording it for later.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:51.88,0:05:53.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}又是这个信号\N{\rENG}It's the signal again.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.32,0:05:54.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}橄榄石!\N{\rENG}Peridot.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}珍珠,信号又出现了!\N{\rENG}Pearl, the signal is back.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:56.05,0:05:57.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}又一次?\N{\rENG}Again?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们得回去\N{\rENG}We need to get back out there.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.34,0:05:59.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好\N{\rENG} Right.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.55,0:06:01.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文,狮子呢?\N{\rENG}Steven, where's Lion?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶,把头从冰箱里收回来\N{\rENG}Amethyst, get your head out of the fridge.\N
Dialogue: 600,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.86,Hint,,0,0,0,,此处“MooMoo Milk”致敬《口袋妖怪》系列中的同名饮料
Dialogue: 100,0:06:02.86,0:06:03.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}出发吧,各位\N{\rENG}Let's go, guys.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:06.50,0:06:07.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我希望你准备好了\N{\rENG}I hope you're ready.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.68,0:06:09.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你知道的\N{\rENG}You know I am.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:10.90,0:06:13.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是什么?返场表演吗?\N{\rENG}What's this -- an encore performance?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:13.97,0:06:16.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还想见到我,不是吗?\N{\rENG}Just couldn't get enough of me, could you?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们在等什么?\N{\rENG}What are we waiting for?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.24,0:06:21.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}表演开始!\N{\rENG}Let the show begin!\N
