Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.46,0:07:20.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}橄榄石已经回来过两次了\N{\rENG}Peridot's been back here twice,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.52,0:07:22.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}显然她还会再来第三次,对吧?\N{\rENG}so the odds are good she'll come back again, right?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}Bam!这样我们就能抓到她了.\N{\rENG}Bam! That's when we'll get her.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对啊,Bam!\N{\rENG}Yeah. Bam!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:26.54,0:07:28.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴肯定会有另眼相看\N{\rENG}Garnet will be so impressed.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后她会觉得我酷回来了!\N{\rENG}And then she'll think I'm cool again!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.82,0:07:35.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Mm-hmm.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.58,0:07:37.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没有...\N{\rENG}Nothing...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还是没有...\N{\rENG}More nothing...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.64,0:07:42.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊!她在那!\N{\rENG} There she is!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:42.64,0:07:45.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,等等,那只是个奇怪的仙人掌\N{\rENG}No, wait. That's just a weird cactus.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我觉得她不会来了\N{\rENG}I don't think she's coming.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.98,0:07:51.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...你在干嘛?\N{\rENG}Uh, what are you doing?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:51.73,0:07:53.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果你让你的眼睛失焦,看起来\N{\rENG}If you make your eyes blurry, it looks like\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.46,0:07:55.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}两根手指尖出现了一根魔法香肠\N{\rENG}there's a little magic sausage between your fingers.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:56.04,0:07:57.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真是蠢爆了\N{\rENG}This is stupid.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.18,0:07:58.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这根本没用\N{\rENG}It doesn't even work\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.58,0:07:59.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这样\N{\rENG}Try this.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:59.51,0:08:01.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿,别乱搞我的...哦～\N{\rENG}Hey, don't mess with my -- oh!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:03.18,0:08:05.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然,即使我们没抓到橄榄石\N{\rENG}Well, even if we didn't catch Peridot,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}至少我教你了一种挥霍时间的好方法\N{\rENG}at least I taught you a great way to pass the time.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.12,0:08:09.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}蛤?\N{\rENG} What?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.92,0:08:11.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我感觉看到了什么\N{\rENG}I think I saw something.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.50,0:08:13.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是橄榄石的逃生舱\N{\rENG}It's Peridot's escape pod.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.46,0:08:15.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她修好了?\N{\rENG}She fixed it somehow?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我还以为在我们手里\N{\rENG}But I thought we had it.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.66,0:08:18.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她从神庙里偷出来的?\N{\rENG}Did she steal it from the temple?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:18.82,0:08:21.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔,她在用逃生舱搬运柱子\N{\rENG}Whoa. She's lifting the pillar guys.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后...她在修复通讯中枢\N{\rENG}And she's fixing the hub.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.84,0:08:26.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她在上面做什么?\N{\rENG}What's she doing up there?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.68,0:08:27.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}放大\N{\rENG}Enhance.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.22,0:08:31.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿,不知为什么,橄榄石看起来有点像...\N{\rENG}Hey, for some reason, Peridot kind of looks like...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.80,0:08:32.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}珍珠?\N{\rENG}Pearl?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}蛤?让我看看\N{\rENG}What?! Let me see.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,天哪\N{\rENG}Oh, no.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.44,0:08:42.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么珍珠要重建通讯中枢?\N{\rENG}Why would Pearl rebuild the hub?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.20,0:08:45.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也许她在试着了解它是如何工作的?\N{\rENG}Maybe she's trying to study how it works?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.45,0:08:46.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不是\N{\rENG}No.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:46.56,0:08:47.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不觉得是这样\N{\rENG}I don't think that's it.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:47.96,0:08:50.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也许她是在试着添加更多的频道?\N{\rENG}Maybe she's trying to get us more channels?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.08,0:08:53.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦!\N{\rENG} Oh!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这可不好\N{\rENG}This is no good.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有什么不对吗?\N{\rENG}W-what's wrong?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.97,0:08:58.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是橄榄石\N{\rENG}It's Peridot.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:58.40,0:09:01.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她肯定又修复了通讯中枢\N{\rENG}She must have fixed the communication hub again.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.57,0:09:02.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴...\N{\rENG}Garnet...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:02.50,0:09:03.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}通讯中枢又出事了\N{\rENG}It's the hub again.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她躲过了我的预知能力\N{\rENG}She's evading my future vision.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:05.76,0:09:08.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不管试多少次,我都没法看见我们抓到橄榄石\N{\rENG}No matter how many times I try, I can't see us finding Peridot.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}快点,各位\N{\rENG} Come on, team.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不敢相信橄榄石带给我们这么多麻烦\N{\rENG}I can't believe Peridot is giving us so much trouble.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但这不算什么,对吗,石榴?\N{\rENG}But it hardly matters, right, Garnet?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们能破坏这座塔\N{\rENG}We can disable this tower\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.02,0:09:21.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不管要多少次,只要我们一起,对吧?\N{\rENG}as many times as we need to together, okay?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧.我准备好了\N{\rENG}Okay. I'm ready.\N
Dialogue: 50,0:09:22.49,0:09:23.26,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}你准备好了吗,石榴?\N{\rENG_BKG}Are you ready, Garnet?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道她在做什么\N{\rENG}I know what she's doing. You do?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.02,0:09:24.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真的?\N{\rENG}You do?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.22,0:09:27.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}停下!\N{\rENG}Stop!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有什么不对劲吗,紫晶?\N{\rENG}Is something the matter, Amethyst?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你-你不该这样\N{\rENG}You -- you shouldn't.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.53,0:09:34.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}珍珠,我们看到你了\N{\rENG}Pearl, we saw you.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.16,0:09:35.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊?\N{\rENG}What?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:36.10,0:09:38.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你得告诉石榴是你\N{\rENG}You need to tell Garnet it was you.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一脸蒙b\N{\rENG}I don't understand.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:41.78,0:09:42.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对不起\N{\rENG}I'm sorry.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:43.20,0:09:47.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这...只是...跟你一起成为红玛瑙真的很有趣\N{\rENG}It's just so much fun being sardonyx with you.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}怪不得我看不到我们找到橄榄石\N{\rENG}That's why I couldn't see us finding Peridot.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.29,0:09:52.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等,听我解释\N{\rENG}Wait. Let me explain.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.89,0:09:54.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是你一直在修复通讯中枢!\N{\rENG}You've been fixing the hub!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:55.06,0:09:56.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真的是橄榄石...\N{\rENG}It really was Peridot...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:56.72,0:09:57.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}第一次时\N{\rENG}The first time.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.92,0:09:59.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你骗了我\N{\rENG}You tricked me.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.43,0:10:00.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,不不不不,\N{\rENG}No. No, no, no, no.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.38,0:10:02.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,我们只是需要个融合的理由\N{\rENG}No, we just needed a reason to fuse.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.52,0:10:05.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我只想和你多分享几次胜利而已\N{\rENG}I just wanted to share a few more victories with you.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那些不是胜利\N{\rENG}Those weren't victories.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等,石榴\N{\rENG}Wait, Garnet.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.40,0:10:10.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你看,我们相比你要弱小太多\N{\rENG}You know, we're so much weaker than you.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.50,0:10:13.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}和你融合是我们感觉变强的一个\N{\rENG}Fusing with you is like our one chance to feel...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.16,0:10:14.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}机会\N{\rENG}Stronger.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不要庇护她\N{\rENG}Garnet: Don't defend her.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}橄榄石就在地球上某处,\N{\rENG}Peridot is out there somewhere,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:16.82,0:10:19.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而珍珠一直在分散我们的注意力...就因为些破事!\N{\rENG}and Pearl's been distracting us with nothing.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.02,0:10:22.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴...够了\N{\rENG}Garnet... That's enough.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶,跟我融合\N{\rENG}Amethyst, fuse with me.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:24.62,0:10:25.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但...\N{\rENG}But...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.65,0:10:28.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让我们赶紧结束这一切吧\N{\rENG}Let's just get this over with.\N
Dialogue: 600,0:10:33.75,0:10:36.00,Hint,,0,0,0,,此处苏纪石的出拳动作受《大力水手》的Twister-Sock Punch与《任天堂全明星大乱斗》中大金刚的Giant Punch启发
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}求求你原谅我吧\N{\rENG}Please forgive me.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我当然会原谅你啦\N{\rENG}Of course I forgive you.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的天\N{\rENG}Man.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:11:03.93,0:11:05.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}该有多好啊,\N{\rENG}It sure would be nice\N
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.36,0:11:08.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果这能跟动画一样轻松解决\N{\rENG}if things worked out the way they do in cartoons.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:11:08.30,0:11:08.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是啊\N{\rENG}Yeah.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:11:09.74,0:11:10.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果的话\N{\rENG}It would.\N
